dct_title_s: Geōtechnikos chartēs tēs Helladas = Engineering geological map of Greece / Engineering Geology Department (IGME) ; compilation of the engineering geological map: B. Andronopoulos ; I. Theodossiou-Drandaki ; [and others]. (Sheet 3)
